{"tid":237701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[平反] HKUSPACE厹借刀反遭起底事件後續","createTime":"2017-05-10T14:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T15:19:14.000Z","uid":10533,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"36092b32657e127419b9f981de9b287fa7510118","tid":237701,"uid":10533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:14:06.000Z","msg":"舊po link: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/230290/page/33?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/230290/page/33?ref=ios</a><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n被爆上黎後 Alvin仔宣稱要報驚<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">alvin仔不願面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user-615549674/2017-05-09-audio-00003233\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fuser-615549674%2F2017-05-09-audio-00003233&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TagRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=13942068\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/user-615549674/2017-05-09-audio-00003233</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user-615549674/2017-05-09-audio-00003232\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fuser-615549674%2F2017-05-09-audio-00003232&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2TagRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=9ccc0f7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/user-615549674/2017-05-09-audio-00003232</a></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">出黎行預左要還啦 <br />\n當初點解你要爆兩個無關痛癢嘅女仔出黎？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y6D9m65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY6D9m65.jpg&h=af222060&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/10/220512_46113f22705d5aca4143726c90fa3e20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F10%2F220512_46113f22705d5aca4143726c90fa3e20.jpg&h=0ad44b69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/10/220513_2b10a97b49cfc58b23584a739dc38def.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F10%2F220513_2b10a97b49cfc58b23584a739dc38def.jpg&h=1278863a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝伯賢巴整合<br />\n<br />\n等我嚟整合啦 講故台 走甜<br />\n第一次寫故 唔好屌<br />\n主要有兩條線<br />\n主線係樓主佳叔賭波章<br />\n樓主就同佳叔有恩怨 放佳叔ig相上連登借刀 相中波及Kary妹妹 有巴打求Kary ig 粉色放K ig 及7相一張並負上caption狗也不 事件引起K不滿 心怒之 並引發其後分支事件<br />\n出住先反應好再出<br />\n支線 kary復仇記章<br />\n承接上文 Kary立即與友人相討事件 經過一連串的起底行動 發現粉兄曾發文自稱6月1生日 以及在下隔床訓覺 並得出結論粉兄乃Alvin仔 心怒之<br />\n支線續~ 友人以落街買撈發文 &quot;公開Alvin仔疑似溝女對話 對話內容大致上講述alvin仔對XXX展開噓寒問暖的wtsapp對話 而XXX冇show Alvin仔&quot; 為Kary報復 並聲稱上述事件為狗公行為 要推到Alvin女朋友上嚟 其後更將Alvin仔資料包括ig fb工作地點 一一公開<br />\n主線續~樓主無視眾人目光 仍然自high放出大量佳叔寫真 並以惡言抹黑 其間粉兄搭話指 佳叔曾對自己best fd Natalie展開追求<br />\n其後Natalie亦被樓主公開個人照 令Natalie中槍<br />\n主線&quot;樓主佳叔賭波篇&quot;基本上完 支線配角唔跟劇情走臨時搶戲份 豈料觀眾反應極好 令收線直線上升 導演臨時要求加戲拍kary復仇記章<br />\n<br />\n其間alvin仔朋友(樓主應該係)利用多一個ac<br />\n(吳若系)(#87031)追擊撈巴出言 借你老母刀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴打有補充？"},{"pid":"b3c8f112487d870cd1074ca475898741c22b2dcc","tid":237701,"uid":10533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e4a2fdd0a6e28b9ef8360c595a2829c29017d5","tid":237701,"uid":10533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 消滅借刀文化 你我有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8704d15e6654b05775e8aefdf68caef3dba4fa","tid":237701,"uid":10533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:25:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cl